Thank so much for watching my first tutorial!!!!! 💙💚
Quick guide and tips to setting up a simple 4’x4’ space with Flora Stackers on the micro drip set up - with the new parallel 4-way emitters!

Shown here is 4” to 6” Flora Stackers but there are 6” to 8” as well for those already rocking 6” cubes 

FloraFlex offers a ton of options to the grower with all mediums, I’ll be show casing the different methods they provide and , don’t forget I’ve been hooked up with codes to help you save 💰💰 - #cannabiscultivation #womengrow #shegrowscannabis #plantsoverpills #cannabisismedicine #plantsheal #cannabisculture #cannabiscultivator #womeninweed #womenandweed #womangrown #cannabisgrow #cannabis101 #supportwomenownedbusinesses #cannabiscultivation101 #highsociety #highsociety420 #radreefer #floraflex #fulltilt #bulkyB

node.text:
Damn yooo! I slapped this beast together in under 10 min! So without a doubt, if I can do it, you can do it! 

@floraflex coming in clutch - 🚀🚀 I’ll be at HQ tomorrow to go live with some Q&A 

Couple of frequently asked questions- 

Straight tube: warm up our tubes in the sun to work out the curve on the roll 

Holes: flip the hole puncher around so it’s facing you and u can see wtf you’re punching instead of looking over the shoulder of the puncher lol 

Drippers: only put them in a few inches deep into the medium, water will work down, if you force it too deep the upper layer of coco won’t receive as much water as you presumed lol 

We learned that plants that have been hand watered in veg take readjusting if you’re hooking them up to irrigation only in flower - two completely different watering styles so that should be taken into consideration 

Don’t forget they’ve set me up with discount codes to pass on the savings to yall 💙💙

node.text:
Duuuude! Like butter YO
Have you even seen a @growglide garden??? Wait till the end!

Those @GrowGlide Triple stacked capabilities- do you think this is the future of indoor growing? Why or why not?

To 👏 The 👏 MOON 

I’m still mindblown 🤯 from last weeks’ experience walking into my first vertical garden - quite literally a moment I’ll never forget!!
 
It’s still hard to wrap my head around it sheer capabilities behind a project like that- Can’t wait to load these up with those new @floraflex LEDs 
🌞 🌞 🌞

Evenly dispersed water on a consistent basis is a total game changer from hand watering. 
Humans are a finicky thing lol- 

Finding the @royalgoldsoil and FloraFlex Nutrients combo most excellent- 

I’m looking forward to getting another round of 1Gal coco in the next round-

node.text:
Throw back to a few seasons ago - 
Just smashing these spaces out the park… apparently for nothing more than experience and a good story - like most of us who share the “I still need to get paid” card. 🤦🏻‍♀️ I did meet some amazing people though 🖤🖤🖤

This might have been one of the heaviest  ladies I’d ever taken down at that point, I’m holding her top for her in my other hand ☺️
Those SoCal mountains sure gave me a run for my money - lots of sweat and tears (blood just kinda happens expectedly) and lessons learned from failed partnerships. Lessons I’m STILL learning today- many chapters later. 
Ain’t it some shit lookin back 🤔🤣🤓

node.text:
*licks finger*
*Touches arm*
Tsssss. Hot lol 
But for real tho, how many of you are guilty of thinking you aren’t skilled enough to pull it off? 

Stahp that shit right now, 
How about thinking about what happens when you do pull it off??????

Me too tho yo, I’m like- can I even manage to perform in this kind of a space??? 
Yes the Fuck you can
Period.
